  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You conjure spirits from the Elemental Planes that flit around you in a 15-foot Emanation for the duration. Until the spell ends, any attack you make deals an extra 2d8 damage when you hit a creature in the Emanation. This damage is Acid, Cold, Fire, or Lightning (your choice when you make the attack).</p><p>In addition, the ground in the Emanation is &amp;Reference[DifficultTerrain] for your enemies.</p><p><strong>Using a Higher-Level Spell Slot.</strong> The damage increases by 2d8 for each spell slot level above 4.</p>",
